dmca.title: Tribal secretary complains of defamation, copyright infringement
dmca.body:
Dear Blogger Support, 

My name is [private] and I am the Tribal Secretary for The Munsee Delaware Indian Nation-USA. I had previously contacted you via e-mail (9/5/05) about an offensive site on your server. Your response was for me to write you a letter. My first issue is with your saying,
dmca.principal_name: Tribal Secretary for The Munsee Delaware Indian Nation-USA
